7ce zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 zaufanie do Twojego produktu i przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 nowych kupuj\u0105cych.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, restocking to nie tylko dodanie produktu do magazynu, ale tak\u017ce strategia, kt\u00f3ra wymaga przemy\u015blenia i dzia\u0142ania. Stosuj\u0105c powy\u017csze wskaz\u00f3wki, zwi\u0119kszysz swoje szanse na sukces i przywr\u00f3cenie widoczno\u015bci swojego produktu.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak skutecznie restockowa\u0107 produkt na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy kiedykolwiek zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak na<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4281,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4280","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4280"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4280"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4280\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4281"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4280"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4280"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4280"}],"curies":[{"name":